item.title: IRON CTF 2024
item.description: IRON CTF 2024 Description Welcome to the inaugural edition of IRON CTF (Intrusion Reconnaissance and Offensive Navigation CTF)! Team 1nf1n1ty from SASTRA Deemed University invites you to embark on an exciting online Jeopardy-style Capture the Flag challenge. Whether you’re just starting out or a seasoned hacker, this event promises the perfect platform to push your limits, hone your skills, and enjoy the thrill of competition. Tackle diverse challenges in categories like Web Exploitation, Game Hacking, Reverse Engineering, Cryptography, Forensics, Binary Exploitation, and more.
